    "description": "Shadow Dash is a retro 2D action platformer with PIXEL-ART characters on OIL PAINTING backgrounds and changing game controls.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/06c8d4d6906974426415eb283dcc5a3e.avif?t=1758659009\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>In this challenging, gorgeous, and fun old-school arcade game, you are possessed by a demon and you only have a limited amount of time to hunt down and catch the MAGIC ORB that floats through the stage. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/a7d947dbe27eb4e101a712fe20e0bfa4.poster.avif?t=1758659009\" width=720 height=576 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/a7d947dbe27eb4e101a712fe20e0bfa4.webm?t=1758659009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>DOUBLE-JUMP to avoid obstacles and FIRE your own shadow to defeat enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/190aea2482cfda8e24def470aaea6799.avif?t=1758659009\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>If you fail to beat the ten-second countdown in every level, you’re POSSESSED and the CONTROLS are REVERSED and you’re a bit FASTER - but only for another ten seconds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/0efb1f3d1eba5071597d2691c151e6d6.poster.avif?t=1758659009\" width=542 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/0efb1f3d1eba5071597d2691c151e6d6.webm?t=1758659009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Make sure to always catch that orb and discover the exciting story of your adventure.<br><br>We are looking forward to hearing your feedback!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/abdef73a21fba154e6fac91b71b63d9c.avif?t=1758659009\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><strong>Main Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gorgeous visuals: pixel art characters in oil-painted backgrounds<br></li><li>Changing game controls<br></li><li>Discover the surprising origins of your possession and how you can save yourself <br></li><li>90s arcade &amp; console (SNES - MD/Genesis) game feel<br></li><li>Challenging &amp; fun<br></li><li>Short (1-4 hours)</li></ul>",
